title: Did the senior vice president of the Motava Calles program decide to cancel Roseanne?
subtitle: The Senior Vice-President of the Mutava Cables programme did not cancel the rebooted theatrical comedo because the Senior Vice-President of the Mutava Calais programme did not exist.
author: Dan Evon
vclaim: The decision to cancel the Roseanne program was taken by the vice president of the Motava Calais program.
